&lt;h1&gt;Looking for an additional role!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Have you ever thought about working within a prison?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you enjoy being part of a team in a diverse and ever-changing environment?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for a Bank Registered Nurse within HMP Warren Hill situated in Woodbridge, Suffolk&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Working as a Bank Registered Nurse offers you flexibility and workplace variety. You would also be assisting the wider permanent team, covering for planned and unplanned absences&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a qualified Registered Nurse (Adult) with a real passion for developing your clinical skills in an environment that is ever changing.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; If you are self-motivated and able to work autonomously as well as showing plenty of initiative when it comes to handling a wide range of situations, then this could be the right role for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In return for your hard work you will receive...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Practice Plus Group, we are proud to support our employees with continued professional development opportunities and further education (subject to service needs). Staff are encouraged to develop skills and learning to contribute to the ever-changing needs of our specific client groups. Other benefits include cycle to work scheme, on-site gym facilities and free onsite parking at some locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Further job information…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; This is a bank vacancy with variable hours, as required. The maximum rate for the role is £19.73 per hour, depending on experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Please note that offers of employment are subject to Practice Plus Group Terms &amp; Conditions and receipt of satisfactory references, an enhanced DBS check and prison vetting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Practice Plus Group, we actively promote diversity and equal opportunities.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
